with how something works.


11
00:00:27.194 --> 00:00:30.664 line:-2
[Monika] App and game design
enables our device


12
00:00:30.697 --> 00:00:33.367 line:-2
to be what it is
and what it can become


13
00:00:33.400 --> 00:00:34.468 line:-1
in your hands.


14
00:00:34.501 --> 00:00:36.537 line:-1
♪ ♪


15
00:00:36.570 --> 00:00:38.338 line:-2
[Heena] Designing an app
or a game


