00:00:38.372 --> 00:00:41.041 line:-2
is actually
quite an intimate experience.


17
00:00:41.074 --> 00:00:43.243 line:-2
[Teo]
I need to empathize.


18
00:00:43.277 --> 00:00:45.712 line:-2
I need to have some--
try and understand


