00:01:05.599 --> 00:01:07.367 line:-2
are the ones
that usually stand out.


29
00:01:07.401 --> 00:01:14.408 line:-1
♪ ♪


30
00:01:16,109 --> 00:01:18,545
[Alan] For us to celebrate
the best of the best,


