00:01:18,579 --> 00:01:21,248
those apps that were designed
in such a way


32
00:01:21,281 --> 00:01:23,217
that are deserving
of an Apple Design Award,


33
00:01:23.250 --> 00:01:24.251 line:-1
you know, nothing is bigger


34
00:01:24.284 --> 00:01:26.186 line:-2
in this community,
in our community.


35
00:01:26,220 --> 00:01:27,554
[James]
It's always easy to remember


