132
00:05:40,974 --> 00:05:44,578
[Andre] Delight and fun
is when you use all of the tools


133
00:05:44,611 --> 00:05:48,315
at your disposal
in an unexpected way.


134
00:05:48,348 --> 00:05:49,783
[Lynne] I think the reason
that it's important


135
00:05:49,816 --> 00:05:51,618
is because it's really memorable
for people.


136
00:05:51,652 --> 00:05:54,354
People understand
that using the app


137
00:05:54,388 --> 00:05:56,823
that time
kind of brightened up your day.


138
00:05:56,857 --> 00:05:58,559
They're gonna return to it


139
00:05:58,592 --> 00:06:00,227
and use it
again and again and again.


140
00:06:00,260 --> 00:06:03,797
[Allan] For a game,
what really stands out


141
00:06:03,830 --> 00:06:06,633
in terms of delight and fun
a lot of the time


142
00:06:06,667 --> 00:06:08,936
are these moments in the game.


143
00:06:08,969 --> 00:06:11,738
Maybe it's something
that catches you by surprise


144
00:06:11,772 --> 00:06:13,674
and just creates
this little moment of,


145
00:06:13,707 --> 00:06:15,475
like, "Oh, I love that."


146
00:06:15,509 --> 00:06:17,878
[Teo] People are
seeking experiences


147
00:06:17,911 --> 00:06:20,280
where they can escape
a lot of the time,


148
00:06:20,314 --> 00:06:21,815
things that might
make you laugh,


149
00:06:21,849 --> 00:06:24,351
make you smile,
and just have fun.


150
00:06:24,384 --> 00:06:26,019
[chuckles]


151
00:06:26,053 --> 00:06:29,489
[Allan] The winner
