00:08:03.684 --> 00:08:05.118 line:-1
There's an action and reaction,


183
00:08:05.152 --> 00:08:09.990 line:-2
and that dance
is where interaction stands.


184
00:08:10.023 --> 00:08:12.593 line:-2
[Caroline]
Ooh, look, parallax.


185
00:08:12,626 --> 00:08:18,265
[Alan] Interaction is all about
how an app or a game works,


186
00:08:18,298 --> 00:08:19,833
how the user relates to it,


187
00:08:19,867 --> 00:08:21,702
how they make their way
through the application


188
00:08:21,735 --> 00:08:22,970
and experience it.


189
00:08:23,003 --> 00:08:25,339
In our world,
nothing's more critical.


190
00:08:25,372 --> 00:08:28,375
[Jon] Interaction always has
a result to what you do


191
00:08:28,408 --> 00:08:30,644
even if the result
is letting you know


192
00:08:30,677 --> 00:08:31,812
nothing happened.


193
00:08:31,845 --> 00:08:34,815
[Doug] Apps that stand out
in the Interaction category


