00:09:00,474 --> 00:09:01,441
It becomes invisible.


204
00:09:01,475 --> 00:09:02,809
[Lauren] When you're interacting
with a game,


205
00:09:02,843 --> 00:09:05,179
and you are just
seamlessly moving,


206
00:09:05,212 --> 00:09:09,049
and you're not thinking,
