00:09:09,082 --> 00:09:10,884
I am moving
my right thumb down."


208
00:09:10,918 --> 00:09:13,086
It's just--it is intuitive.


209
00:09:13,120 --> 00:09:14,855
You just understand
what you're gonna need to do.


210
00:09:14,888 --> 00:09:16,523
You feel like you're at one


211
00:09:16,557 --> 00:09:18,525
with the device
that you're holding,


212
00:09:18,559 --> 00:09:22,196
and it just becomes
second nature.


213
00:09:23.597 --> 00:09:25.566 line:-2
[Doug] The winner
in the Interaction category


214
00:09:25.599 --> 00:09:28.669 line:-1
