00:10:10.410 --> 00:10:12.679 line:-2
you can dial it down
a little bit.


231
00:10:12.713 --> 00:10:14.414 line:-2
[person]
And now all the way up.


232
00:10:14.448 --> 00:10:15.415 line:-2
[Doug]
Okay.


233
00:10:15.449 --> 00:10:17.784 line:-2
Well, there may be
unprintable words in there,


234
00:10:17.818 --> 00:10:18.852 line:-1
but we'll see.


235
00:10:22,189 --> 00:10:23,957
[Lauren] The winner
in the games category


