239
00:10:32.866 --> 00:10:36.336 line:-1
because it is so easy to use.


240
00:10:36.370 --> 00:10:37.838 line:-2
You instantly know
what you're doing


241
00:10:37.871 --> 00:10:40.040 line:-2
when you launch the game.
