00:11:45,105 --> 00:11:47,841
and voices
that are not often heard.


268
00:11:47,875 --> 00:11:50,677
[Caroline] I think there's lots
of ideas still out there


269
00:11:50,711 --> 00:11:54,214
about how technology
can impact social change.


270
00:11:54,248 --> 00:11:56,350
[Mark] A couple ways that we
think about social impact


271
00:11:56,383 --> 00:11:59,520
is does it improve lives
