272
00:11:59,553 --> 00:12:01,922
Does it have lasting value
or impact


273
00:12:01,955 --> 00:12:03,290
on the community as a whole?


274
00:12:04,925 --> 00:12:07,794
[Mike] The winning app
in the Social Impact category


275
00:12:07,828 --> 00:12:10,264
is Be My Eyes.


276
00:12:10,297 --> 00:12:11,498
Be My Eyes won


277
00:12:11,532 --> 00:12:13,400
because it's so clear


278
00:12:13,433 --> 00:12:15,469
the benefit
