303
00:13:19.099 --> 00:13:20.634 line:-1
terrific experience.


304
00:13:20.667 --> 00:13:27.674 line:-1
♪ ♪


305
00:13:28,942 --> 00:13:30,410
[Pablo] The visuals
and the graphics


